Assignment 9 - Use an AI-based tool to generate simple video animations.

Stable Diffusion with AnimateDiff

Step 1: Install Dependencies
Step 2: Load Stable Diffusion Model - Use Stable Diffusion from diffusers library.
Step 3: Generate Frames - Generate image frames for animation.
Step 4: Convert Frames to Video - Use imageio to convert frames into a video.
Step 5: Download the Video - download your video from Colab.
